data.description: Stunning 3 Bed, 2 Bath End Unit Condo w/ Garage in Gated Community! This beautiful 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom end unit is nestled in a secure gated community, offering the perfect blend of luxury, comfort, and privacy.This condo is a gem with its spacious and bright interior featuring vaulted ceilings that create an airy and welcoming ambiance. Step inside to discover the newly painted walls that add a fresh and modern touch throughout the home. The condo boasts three generous bedrooms, providing ample space for you and guests with brand new carpet.The kitchen is a chef's delight with sleek countertops and a breakfast bar perfect for quick meals. The open-concept living and kitchen area create a seamless flow, making it ideal for gatherings. As part of a gated community, residents have access to a range of amenities, including pickle ball, basketball, bocce, and tennis course, a sparkling swimming pool, kids park, club house beautifully landscaped communal areas, creating a resort-like experience every day. Water and basic cable are included in HOA and Remember insurance and taxes are lower which offset the HOA fees.
